{"tid":2405599,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS5 用戶投訴  DualSense 手掣出現飄移問題","createTime":"2021-02-12T13:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T02:06:43.000Z","uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed886413f357523f380a47552927a5ec98b88e7","tid":2405599,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"PlayStation 5 上市短短數月已經售出超過 400 萬部，而且還經常斷市，成績可謂相當理想。未知是否趕製的緣故，PS5 的 DualSense 手掣卻被玩家批評質量欠佳。遊戲手掣的按鈕長期使用，有機會出現磨損或損壞，這些都是玩家們意料之內，不過 PS5 玩家投訴 DualSense 手掣在短時間内出現飄移問題。<br />\n<br />\n所謂遊戲手掣飄移問題，就是當玩家沒有觸碰手掣的任何按鈕，遊戲中的角色都會自己移動。數年前當任天堂 Switch 剛剛推出不久，其 Joy-Con 手掣亦出現過類似問題。好消息是有問題的 DualSense 手掣還在保養期內，Sony 會負責維修或更換；壞消息則是用戶要聯絡 Sony 安排保修，而且在其間無法使用，除非你有另一個備用。<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：ubergizmo<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1144/27743/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1144%2F27743%2F1%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=cd6c5571\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1144/27743/1/</a>"},{"pid":"2d12881a0ac1f0825678856b56bafcb9c917ce2b","tid":2405599,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"連燈仔: 2021年啦, 第一水驚閪?"},{"pid":"df9b1cff29acfb2ed81f2989f22c3b055dff585c","tid":2405599,"uid":52824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2d12881a0ac1f0825678856b56bafcb9c917ce2b","tid":2405599,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"連燈仔: 2021年啦, 第一水驚閪?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T23:22:15.000Z","msg":"未出就諗唔諗買第一水<br />\n出左就想買第一水都買唔到"},{"pid":"3e48092dcdf96744dc7253ef7d8a5eba1dec921c","tid":2405599,"uid":17402,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d12881a0ac1f0825678856b56bafcb9c917ce2b","tid":2405599,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"連燈仔: 2021年啦, 第一水驚閪?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T00